---
title: Warming Cauliflower and Lentil Dal with Green Beans and Toasted Naan Bread
description: The perfect meal for cooler weather, this stick-to-your-ribs dish is veggie and flavour packed. The addition of naan bread rounds it out allowing you to scoop up every last bit.
